en_225446_0	The Ceylon Teachers' Service Union stated that it has decided to temporarily suspend the strike which was planned to be held across schools island wide from the 7th to 11th of this month.
en_225446_1	The General Secretary of the union Mahinda Jayasinghe told the Hiru news team that this decision was taken until an agreement is reached after discussing the solutions offered by the Cabinet yesterday, regarding their salary anomalies.
